public class ProgressMeasure
extends java.util.TreeMap<State,​java.lang.Integer>
This class provides an implementation of progress measures with the domains limited to one level in run DAGs. Such measures are states of the quasi measure automata in [Kla91].
Author:
"Ming-Hsien Tsai"
